          "responseOriginal": "Hi [Name],\n\nOn April 14th we moved from TUNE Pay to Social Snowball.\n\n• Commissions earned in TUNE: Still paid per TUNE's schedule — nothing lost.\n• Sales from April 14th onwards: Social Snowball only.\n• Your dashboard: https://affiliates.socialsnowball.io/auth/affiliate/login\n\nPayout method not set up in SS yet? Do it now — Payout Methods tab, add PayPal or bank details.\n\nWith Health,\n[Your name]\nThe Affiliates Team @ IM8 Health",
